1
00:00:00,680 --> 00:00:03,480
♪Shrugging off past burdens♪

2
00:00:03,480 --> 00:00:06,070
♪Beneath the mask, who am I?♪

3
00:00:06,740 --> 00:00:10,140
♪Release and find wider shores♪

4
00:00:11,840 --> 00:00:14,850
♪Love's a riddle, and rain pours heavy♪

5
00:00:15,220 --> 00:00:17,750
♪Crossed paths, now downward fall♪

6
00:00:18,090 --> 00:00:21,530
♪From dust arises starlight's spark♪

7
00:00:23,280 --> 00:00:28,500
♪Tearing through
the night's dense blockade♪

8
00:00:29,180 --> 00:00:34,260
♪Heart's flame illuminates all solitude♪

9
00:00:35,060 --> 00:00:37,550
♪Let time's sails drift endlessly♪

10
00:00:37,550 --> 00:00:40,160
♪Through wandering exile♪

11
00:00:40,680 --> 00:00:47,940
♪Breaking free from the cocoon,
I start anew♪

12
00:00:48,910 --> 00:00:51,670
♪Moon as song, life as flame♪

13
00:00:51,730 --> 00:00:54,570
♪Nameless heart clings fiercely♪

14
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:55,890
♪Let me♪

15
00:00:56,080 --> 00:01:00,160
♪Charge toward the next raging river♪

16
00:01:00,610 --> 00:01:03,290
♪Moon darts, snow falls♪

17
00:01:03,580 --> 00:01:06,280
♪We tread rugged paths to reunite♪

18
00:01:06,450 --> 00:01:07,920
♪Hands held tight♪

19
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:12,090
♪We forever live for love's sake♪

20
00:01:12,450 --> 00:01:22,700
♪Shadow's spear burns fiercely♪

21
00:01:24,130 --> 00:01:29,680
=Legend of The Female General=

22
00:01:29,880 --> 00:01:31,740
(Xianchang Academy)

23
00:01:31,850 --> 00:01:32,530
Today

24
00:01:33,410 --> 00:01:35,530
(Year 14 of Qingyuan, Wei, Xianchang Academy)
marks your first enrollment.

25
00:01:36,050 --> 00:01:36,810
I know

26
00:01:37,610 --> 00:01:39,009
you come from privileged families

27
00:01:39,810 --> 00:01:42,610
and have lived in comfort till now.

28
00:01:43,770 --> 00:01:44,890
But at Xianchang Academy,

29
00:01:45,610 --> 00:01:47,650
you must study diligently

30
00:01:47,850 --> 00:01:48,810
day and night

31
00:01:49,250 --> 00:01:51,210
to refine your talents
through perseverance

32
00:01:51,970 --> 00:01:53,170
and serve our nation well.

33
00:01:54,759 --> 00:01:57,330
(Master Wei,
Scholar of Xianchang Academy)

34
00:01:57,330 --> 00:01:58,170
Young man,

35
00:01:58,650 --> 00:01:59,610
what's your name?

36
00:02:00,130 --> 00:02:01,530
Why do you keep wearing a mask?

37
00:02:02,250 --> 00:02:04,850
Constantly hiding your true appearance

38
00:02:05,370 --> 00:02:06,770
is rather rude, don't you think?

39
00:02:11,650 --> 00:02:12,290
Master,

40
00:02:12,730 --> 00:02:13,890
I am He Rufei.

41
00:02:14,770 --> 00:02:16,530
My visage is unsightly,

42
00:02:16,970 --> 00:02:18,290
and I fear startling others.

43
00:02:18,730 --> 00:02:20,329
So I cannot remove this mask.

44
00:02:27,810 --> 00:02:29,090
He's the Xiaos' second son?

45
00:02:29,890 --> 00:02:31,130
His exceptionalness lives up

46
00:02:31,290 --> 00:02:32,170
to his reputation!

47
00:02:32,650 --> 00:02:33,329
Indeed.

48
00:02:41,290 --> 00:02:43,010
I, Xiao Jue, apologize for being late.

49
00:02:43,650 --> 00:02:44,610
Please forgive me.

50
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:50,740
=Episode 2=

51
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:17,850
(Cheng Lisu,
Imperial Medical Bureau's Top Disciple)

52
00:03:17,850 --> 00:03:18,930
The army doesn't tolerate

53
00:03:18,970 --> 00:03:20,090
flashy things,

54
00:03:21,210 --> 00:03:21,770
including you.

55
00:03:28,010 --> 00:03:29,450
I traveled so far to join you.

56
00:03:29,730 --> 00:03:30,650
You treat me like this?

57
00:03:31,050 --> 00:03:32,890
You can go back
for your arranged marriage.

58
00:03:34,850 --> 00:03:35,770
If I could beat you,

59
00:03:36,210 --> 00:03:36,770
I'd have...

60
00:03:38,450 --> 00:03:39,410
beaten you senseless.

61
00:03:40,970 --> 00:03:43,250
Feinu, escort Mr. Cheng out.

62
00:03:44,890 --> 00:03:45,430
Understood.

63
00:03:46,410 --> 00:03:47,050
Would you really

64
00:03:47,050 --> 00:03:47,930
abandon your friend

65
00:03:47,930 --> 00:03:48,730
in need?

66
00:03:49,290 --> 00:03:50,210
Avoiding marriage

67
00:03:51,170 --> 00:03:51,890
won't kill you.

68
00:03:53,210 --> 00:03:54,329
At worst, they'll maim you.

69
00:03:54,650 --> 00:03:55,250
Xiao Jue.

70
00:03:55,890 --> 00:03:56,410
Commander.

71
00:03:58,290 --> 00:03:59,210
Uncle.

72
00:04:00,090 --> 00:04:01,170
We're about the same age.

73
00:04:01,530 --> 00:04:03,090
But you're still my maternal uncle.

74
00:04:03,490 --> 00:04:04,490
Please let me stay.

75
00:04:05,530 --> 00:04:06,170
Okay?

76
00:04:15,410 --> 00:04:15,970
Thank you.

77
00:04:32,730 --> 00:04:34,370
(If you enlist as a woman,)

78
00:04:34,850 --> 00:04:36,010
(it will remain a liability.)

79
00:04:36,850 --> 00:04:37,690
(So I have prepared)

80
00:04:38,010 --> 00:04:38,650
(for you)

81
00:04:38,690 --> 00:04:39,850
(male identity papers)

82
00:04:40,330 --> 00:04:41,210
(of He Yan.)

83
00:04:43,860 --> 00:04:46,010
(He Yan's Household Register)

84
00:04:46,010 --> 00:04:46,890
You're He Yan, right?

85
00:04:48,730 --> 00:04:49,770
(Two names are different)

86
00:04:50,170 --> 00:04:50,930
(in one character.)

87
00:04:51,770 --> 00:04:53,250
(Master's foresight is thoughtful.)

88
00:04:54,370 --> 00:04:55,690
To the left tent for screening.

89
00:04:56,130 --> 00:04:57,530
Then to the right tent if you pass

90
00:04:57,570 --> 00:04:58,210
to register

91
00:04:58,370 --> 00:04:59,290
for uniforms and money.

92
00:05:00,020 --> 00:05:00,730
Thank you.

93
00:05:00,890 --> 00:05:01,450
Next.

94
00:05:03,610 --> 00:05:05,050
Commander, what's screening?

95
00:05:05,810 --> 00:05:06,970
Don't know what screening is?

96
00:05:07,450 --> 00:05:08,010
It's simple.

97
00:05:08,410 --> 00:05:09,850
Strip naked for the medic's exam.

98
00:05:10,330 --> 00:05:11,090
If you're healthy,

99
00:05:11,130 --> 00:05:11,730
you'll pass.

100
00:05:12,490 --> 00:05:13,610
- Thanks.
- Next.

101
00:05:19,530 --> 00:05:20,730
The Gaoxia horse struggles

102
00:05:21,170 --> 00:05:22,210
with the climate.

103
00:05:22,810 --> 00:05:23,770
It hasn't eaten.

104
00:05:24,570 --> 00:05:25,210
Examine it.

105
00:05:25,610 --> 00:05:26,450
See what ails it.

106
00:05:26,810 --> 00:05:27,330
What?

107
00:05:28,170 --> 00:05:29,570
I, a future imperial physician,

108
00:05:29,610 --> 00:05:30,570
am treating a horse?

109
00:05:30,810 --> 00:05:31,810
As a healer,

110
00:05:32,409 --> 00:05:33,970
shouldn't you treat all lives equally?

111
00:05:34,930 --> 00:05:37,250
Besides, Yezhou Garrison
keeps no idlers.

112
00:05:37,810 --> 00:05:38,610
If you want to stay,

113
00:05:39,770 --> 00:05:40,490
be useful.

114
00:05:50,450 --> 00:05:51,570
Fortunately, this is a mare.

115
00:05:52,090 --> 00:05:53,330
Helping it is acceptable.

116
00:05:53,770 --> 00:05:54,570
I'd have declined

117
00:05:54,690 --> 00:05:55,690
if it were a stallion.

118
00:05:56,850 --> 00:05:58,370
Xiao Jue, watch closely.

119
00:05:58,850 --> 00:05:59,730
I can both heal

120
00:05:59,970 --> 00:06:00,810
and tame horses.

121
00:06:14,290 --> 00:06:14,930
Look!

122
00:06:15,410 --> 00:06:16,250
It's spooked!

123
00:06:16,650 --> 00:06:17,250
It's coming!

124
00:06:30,650 --> 00:06:31,290
Make way!

125
00:06:31,650 --> 00:06:32,409
Move aside! Move!

126
00:06:35,050 --> 00:06:35,650
Move aside!

127
00:07:20,130 --> 00:07:21,330
That man's way of taming

128
00:07:22,530 --> 00:07:23,890
is unique to the Fuyue Army.

129
00:07:24,650 --> 00:07:25,650
He's He Rufei's man?

130
00:07:29,490 --> 00:07:31,290
(No, I accidentally gave myself away.)

131
00:07:31,810 --> 00:07:32,810
(Xiao Jue noticed it.)

132
00:07:33,690 --> 00:07:34,210
Not bad.

133
00:07:34,690 --> 00:07:36,170
He resembles my heroics in the past.

134
00:07:39,610 --> 00:07:40,770
That move he just pulled

135
00:07:41,650 --> 00:07:42,810
is way beyond your skills.

136
00:08:03,250 --> 00:08:03,770
(Oh no.)

137
00:08:04,450 --> 00:08:05,930
(Xiao Jue knows Fuyue Army's moves.)

138
00:08:06,770 --> 00:08:07,970
(He definitely recognized it.)

139
00:08:08,330 --> 00:08:09,330
(Yet he didn't react.)

140
00:08:10,850 --> 00:08:11,410
(He took me)

141
00:08:11,450 --> 00:08:12,410
(as He Rufei's man)

142
00:08:13,170 --> 00:08:14,490
(and planned to act against me?)

143
00:08:17,890 --> 00:08:18,410
Come on.

144
00:08:18,650 --> 00:08:19,290
Let's continue.

145
00:08:20,450 --> 00:08:21,050
Gather around!

146
00:08:25,770 --> 00:08:26,410
Impressive.

147
00:08:26,810 --> 00:08:27,450
You're small.

148
00:08:27,490 --> 00:08:28,410
But you're quite good.

149
00:08:28,650 --> 00:08:29,290
You flatter me.

150
00:08:29,650 --> 00:08:30,730
My taming skills could

151
00:08:30,930 --> 00:08:32,289
never match yours, Instructor.

152
00:08:33,820 --> 00:08:34,490
Well...

153
00:08:36,130 --> 00:08:36,890
The army needs

154
00:08:36,890 --> 00:08:37,770
talents like you.

155
00:08:39,370 --> 00:08:40,049
But

156
00:08:40,770 --> 00:08:41,970
I haven't been screened yet.

157
00:08:42,210 --> 00:08:42,970
Forget about it.

158
00:08:43,169 --> 00:08:44,330
If you can tame such a horse,

159
00:08:44,370 --> 00:08:45,610
your physique must be good.

160
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:46,680
I'll secure the horse.

161
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:48,250
Then let's handle the documents. Wait.

162
00:08:48,650 --> 00:08:49,490
- Go.
- Thank you.

163
00:08:50,290 --> 00:08:51,130
So naughty.

164
00:08:51,450 --> 00:08:52,490
Turn and slash!

165
00:08:53,770 --> 00:08:54,690
Since you suspect him,

166
00:08:54,970 --> 00:08:56,010
why not kill him directly

167
00:08:56,130 --> 00:08:56,690
for good?

168
00:08:57,210 --> 00:08:58,650
If he's truly a spy sent

169
00:08:58,650 --> 00:08:59,610
by the ill-intended one,

170
00:09:00,170 --> 00:09:00,890
killing one will

171
00:09:01,570 --> 00:09:02,610
only bring replacements.

172
00:09:03,410 --> 00:09:04,930
Rather than endless trouble,

173
00:09:05,290 --> 00:09:06,210
it's better to keep him

174
00:09:06,930 --> 00:09:08,490
to potentially lure out the mastermind.

175
00:09:09,610 --> 00:09:10,250
I wonder

176
00:09:10,490 --> 00:09:11,850
whether the mastermind is He Rufei

177
00:09:11,850 --> 00:09:12,650
or Xu Jingfu.

178
00:09:13,250 --> 00:09:14,010
You said

179
00:09:14,490 --> 00:09:15,690
before your father's campaign,

180
00:09:16,050 --> 00:09:17,530
he impeached the prime minister.

181
00:09:18,450 --> 00:09:19,250
Within days,

182
00:09:19,490 --> 00:09:20,410
he fell into an ambush

183
00:09:20,530 --> 00:09:21,290
at Mingshui.

184
00:09:21,730 --> 00:09:22,810
He Rufei's troops

185
00:09:22,890 --> 00:09:24,090
were a hundred li away,

186
00:09:24,930 --> 00:09:25,690
but arrived only

187
00:09:25,730 --> 00:09:27,130
on day seven after your father

188
00:09:27,130 --> 00:09:27,930
sent the letter.

189
00:09:28,650 --> 00:09:29,570
It was intentional.

190
00:09:30,250 --> 00:09:30,770
I think

191
00:09:31,250 --> 00:09:32,490
they are birds of a feather.

192
00:09:33,930 --> 00:09:35,410
But we lack concrete evidence.

193
00:09:36,250 --> 00:09:37,130
We can't prove

194
00:09:37,130 --> 00:09:38,170
the defeat at Mingshui

195
00:09:38,450 --> 00:09:40,130
relates to Xu Jingfu and He Rufei.

196
00:09:40,810 --> 00:09:41,610
Nor can we prove

197
00:09:42,250 --> 00:09:43,890
their collusion.

198
00:09:45,650 --> 00:09:47,010
Now the Xiao Army is weakened

199
00:09:47,690 --> 00:09:48,810
and disliked by His Majesty.

200
00:09:49,690 --> 00:09:51,050
We can only investigate covertly.

201
00:09:52,050 --> 00:09:53,210
With troop shortages here

202
00:09:53,210 --> 00:09:54,050
and low funds,

203
00:09:55,250 --> 00:09:56,650
building a competent new army

204
00:09:57,650 --> 00:09:58,530
is highly challenging.

205
00:10:04,370 --> 00:10:05,930
Investigate that man thoroughly.

206
00:10:06,570 --> 00:10:07,490
I want to know

207
00:10:07,650 --> 00:10:08,530
whose pawn he is.

208
00:10:09,770 --> 00:10:10,530
Understood.

209
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:15,600
(Xu Mansion)

210
00:10:32,430 --> 00:10:35,480
(Chu Zhao, Disciple of Xu Jingfu)

211
00:10:44,450 --> 00:10:45,300
Master.

212
00:10:47,130 --> 00:10:48,410
Regarding the Que City mission,

213
00:10:49,250 --> 00:10:50,410
you've worked hard.

214
00:10:51,890 --> 00:10:52,570
As ordered,

215
00:10:53,210 --> 00:10:54,570
I monitored Xiao Jue in Que City.

216
00:10:55,290 --> 00:10:56,570
The battle was unwinnable,

217
00:10:57,170 --> 00:10:58,170
yet no one anticipated

218
00:10:58,450 --> 00:10:59,530
his ruthless tactic

219
00:10:59,650 --> 00:11:00,810
of flooding Que City

220
00:11:01,130 --> 00:11:02,370
to force a reversal.

221
00:11:03,410 --> 00:11:04,050
Pity

222
00:11:05,850 --> 00:11:07,410
those countless lost souls.

223
00:11:09,090 --> 00:11:09,650
Zilan,

224
00:11:09,890 --> 00:11:11,170
ensure that Xiao Jue's

225
00:11:11,330 --> 00:11:12,810
flooding of Que City

226
00:11:13,050 --> 00:11:15,930
and mass slaughter of tens of thousands

227
00:11:16,650 --> 00:11:18,010
are publicly exposed

228
00:11:18,250 --> 00:11:21,090
to expose his infamy to the world.

229
00:11:21,370 --> 00:11:22,530
His Majesty's wariness

230
00:11:23,090 --> 00:11:25,250
toward him will grow even deeper.

231
00:11:28,370 --> 00:11:29,490
Though victorious,

232
00:11:30,050 --> 00:11:31,930
he was promoted in name
but demoted in reality.

233
00:11:32,570 --> 00:11:34,210
He was sent to Yezhou Garrison.

234
00:11:34,610 --> 00:11:37,570
Even with his conscription rights
restored,

235
00:11:37,690 --> 00:11:39,330
that desolate wasteland

236
00:11:39,490 --> 00:11:41,530
could never yield decent soldiers.

237
00:11:42,450 --> 00:11:43,090
Moreover,

238
00:11:43,930 --> 00:11:45,050
I discovered in Que City

239
00:11:45,650 --> 00:11:47,090
a fish that slipped through the net.

240
00:11:49,050 --> 00:11:50,850
I've positioned him as a hidden pawn

241
00:11:51,050 --> 00:11:51,850
in our strategy.

242
00:11:52,170 --> 00:11:53,010
Given time,

243
00:11:53,450 --> 00:11:55,770
he'll become an unstoppable vanguard.

244
00:11:58,050 --> 00:11:58,730
Great.

245
00:11:59,010 --> 00:12:01,250
Focus on recovering these coming days.

246
00:12:01,930 --> 00:12:02,650
Soon,

247
00:12:03,090 --> 00:12:04,770
you'll be entrusted

248
00:12:04,810 --> 00:12:05,610
with greater tasks.

249
00:12:05,890 --> 00:12:06,650
Understood.

250
00:12:07,490 --> 00:12:08,010
Chu Zhao.

251
00:12:14,290 --> 00:12:16,890
(Xu Pingting, Daughter of Xu Jingfu)
You're back! Did you bring me a gift?

252
00:12:18,970 --> 00:12:20,730
Your impudence grows by the day.

253
00:12:21,570 --> 00:12:22,260
Father.

254
00:12:23,570 --> 00:12:24,370
I'd never forget.

255
00:12:30,650 --> 00:12:31,570
What fragrance is this?

256
00:12:32,250 --> 00:12:33,090
Try it to find out.

257
00:12:34,010 --> 00:12:34,890
Try it with me.

258
00:12:38,210 --> 00:12:38,970
Go ahead.

259
00:12:40,850 --> 00:12:42,970
Then I'll graciously accept.

260
00:12:43,900 --> 00:12:44,410
Let's go.

261
00:13:01,050 --> 00:13:02,810
What's wrong with this tinderbox?

262
00:13:04,250 --> 00:13:05,010
Let me try.

263
00:13:11,730 --> 00:13:12,370
Stop it.

264
00:13:13,290 --> 00:13:14,410
Light it with the candle.

265
00:13:17,570 --> 00:13:19,130
Burn him! Burn him!

266
00:13:19,210 --> 00:13:20,170
(Burn him!)

267
00:13:33,130 --> 00:13:33,690
Let me see.

268
00:13:36,450 --> 00:13:37,170
You're injured.

269
00:13:40,730 --> 00:13:41,330
Are you okay?

270
00:13:42,210 --> 00:13:42,810
It's nothing.

271
00:13:43,970 --> 00:13:44,810
Just got burned.

272
00:13:45,810 --> 00:13:46,450
My grip slipped.

273
00:14:07,530 --> 00:14:08,050
Young Master,

274
00:14:08,890 --> 00:14:09,530
your injury...

275
00:14:16,050 --> 00:14:17,770
(Yingxiang, Chu Zhao's maid)
I know you wounded your left arm

276
00:14:17,810 --> 00:14:18,690
intentionally.

277
00:14:19,010 --> 00:14:19,570
But...

278
00:14:20,090 --> 00:14:21,250
I've failed my duties.

279
00:14:22,250 --> 00:14:23,650
And I was also injured by refugees.

280
00:14:24,730 --> 00:14:26,770
I feel ashamed, Master.

281
00:14:28,290 --> 00:14:29,850
You're being too harsh with yourself.

282
00:14:30,210 --> 00:14:31,570
To earn Master's favor,

283
00:14:34,970 --> 00:14:36,410
sacrifices must be made.

284
00:15:14,290 --> 00:15:15,290
(A bandit?)

285
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:18,300
(Wang Ba, Yezhou Garrison recruit)

286
00:15:19,770 --> 00:15:20,490
Move!

287
00:15:21,230 --> 00:15:23,130
(Zheng Xuan, Yezhou Garrison recruit)

288
00:15:25,980 --> 00:15:27,130
(Face-tattooing punishment?)

289
00:15:27,730 --> 00:15:28,730
(He was a convict)

290
00:15:29,250 --> 00:15:29,930
(and a rogue.)

291
00:15:29,930 --> 00:15:30,690
Boss, your tea.

292
00:15:32,450 --> 00:15:33,210
Well-mannered.

293
00:15:33,930 --> 00:15:34,530
It's tiring.

294
00:15:39,470 --> 00:15:42,040
(Jiang Jiao, Yezhou Garrison recruit)

295
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:44,310
(Escort Agency)

296
00:15:45,140 --> 00:15:46,360
(Former escort agency member?)

297
00:15:46,490 --> 00:15:47,450
(He must be skilled.)

298
00:15:48,290 --> 00:15:49,010
Look away!

299
00:15:49,570 --> 00:15:50,370
Pretty boy.

300
00:15:51,010 --> 00:15:51,770
(Paler than me.)

301
00:15:52,170 --> 00:15:53,210
(How dare he judge me?)

302
00:15:57,050 --> 00:15:57,890
I used to think

303
00:15:58,090 --> 00:15:59,250
(Mai, Yezhou Garrison recruit)
I was the shortest one here

304
00:15:59,450 --> 00:16:00,370
in the camp.

305
00:16:00,770 --> 00:16:01,370
But now

306
00:16:01,770 --> 00:16:03,010
you're almost as short as me.

307
00:16:03,650 --> 00:16:04,180
Alright.

308
00:16:04,530 --> 00:16:05,530
We together eat more

309
00:16:05,650 --> 00:16:06,450
to grow taller.

310
00:16:06,570 --> 00:16:08,970
By the way, what's your name?

311
00:16:09,370 --> 00:16:09,970
He Yan.

312
00:16:10,690 --> 00:16:13,010
Then I'll call you He.

313
00:16:13,450 --> 00:16:14,140
Agreed.

314
00:16:14,610 --> 00:16:15,370
I'm Mai.

315
00:16:16,850 --> 00:16:17,690
I was a farmer.

316
00:16:17,890 --> 00:16:18,450
Sleep here.

317
00:16:19,560 --> 00:16:22,100
(Huang Xiong, Yezhou Garrison recruit)

318
00:16:23,250 --> 00:16:24,890
(This one was a hunter.)

319
00:16:25,370 --> 00:16:27,610
(A killer wearing prayer beads.)

320
00:16:27,930 --> 00:16:28,730
(Interesting.)

321
00:16:29,610 --> 00:16:30,130
Thanks.

322
00:16:33,050 --> 00:16:33,570
He,

323
00:16:35,330 --> 00:16:36,770
you'll sleep here tonight.

324
00:16:37,170 --> 00:16:38,210
- Okay.
- Let me help.

325
00:16:38,570 --> 00:16:39,370
No need.

326
00:17:09,810 --> 00:17:12,010
You claim hostility with Xiao Jue,

327
00:17:12,329 --> 00:17:13,010
yet you know

328
00:17:13,450 --> 00:17:14,329
the Que City battle

329
00:17:14,609 --> 00:17:16,010
left his reputation in ruins.

330
00:17:16,450 --> 00:17:17,250
Aren't you afraid

331
00:17:18,450 --> 00:17:19,609
to be implicated by him

332
00:17:19,970 --> 00:17:20,770
or slandered?

333
00:17:21,650 --> 00:17:22,250
Master,

334
00:17:23,130 --> 00:17:23,849
I don't believe

335
00:17:24,410 --> 00:17:26,170
Xiao Jue would flood Que City

336
00:17:26,450 --> 00:17:27,730
just for an easy victory.

337
00:17:28,010 --> 00:17:28,650
Nor would he

338
00:17:29,090 --> 00:17:30,850
sacrifice all the people of Que City

339
00:17:31,010 --> 00:17:32,010
as stepping stones

340
00:17:32,610 --> 00:17:34,170
to pave his path to military glory.

341
00:17:35,290 --> 00:17:36,210
Most importantly,

342
00:17:36,570 --> 00:17:39,530
the Xiao Army urgently needs
new recruits right now.

343
00:17:40,650 --> 00:17:43,450
This way I can stand out quicker

344
00:17:44,210 --> 00:17:45,170
and prove myself.

345
00:17:55,890 --> 00:17:57,290
(The snoring chorus is impressive.)

346
00:17:57,910 --> 00:17:59,090
(I last heard this long ago.)

347
00:18:21,970 --> 00:18:22,770
He,

348
00:18:23,610 --> 00:18:24,490
you're up so early.

349
00:18:26,690 --> 00:18:27,250
Nature called.

350
00:18:32,690 --> 00:18:33,330
Mr. Shen.

351
00:18:34,690 --> 00:18:35,730
- Mr. Shen.
- Mr. Shen.

352
00:18:36,170 --> 00:18:39,060
(Shen Han,
Head Instructor of Yezhou Garrison)

353
00:18:47,050 --> 00:18:48,930
What guy...

354
00:18:50,290 --> 00:18:50,970
Mr. Shen.

355
00:18:57,370 --> 00:18:58,570
Good morning, Commander.

356
00:18:58,610 --> 00:18:59,330
- Good morning.
- Good morning.

357
00:18:59,330 --> 00:18:59,900
Good morning.

358
00:19:08,850 --> 00:19:09,650
Up already?

359
00:19:10,770 --> 00:19:12,650
He woke up
from nature's call, Commander.

360
00:19:22,090 --> 00:19:22,770
Everyone!

361
00:19:23,410 --> 00:19:24,570
Gather at the training field

362
00:19:25,130 --> 00:19:27,090
and have ten weighted laps
around the barracks!

363
00:19:27,810 --> 00:19:29,170
Not a single lap less.

364
00:19:29,610 --> 00:19:30,530
Wait, ten...

365
00:19:31,130 --> 00:19:31,810
Ten laps?

366
00:19:32,370 --> 00:19:33,290
Why?

367
00:19:40,930 --> 00:19:42,530
It was all because of you!

368
00:19:44,170 --> 00:19:45,610
You had to be an early riser

369
00:19:46,130 --> 00:19:48,290
with no team spirit!

370
00:19:48,570 --> 00:19:50,250
- Selfish worm!
- Yes, selfish.

371
00:19:50,770 --> 00:19:52,130
Go home if you want to sleep in.

372
00:19:52,730 --> 00:19:53,530
We're in the army.

373
00:19:54,130 --> 00:19:54,770
You...

374
00:19:55,610 --> 00:19:56,450
Boss! Boss!

375
00:19:56,610 --> 00:19:57,930
If you don't get out now,

376
00:19:58,010 --> 00:19:59,050
you'll be punished harder.

377
00:19:59,690 --> 00:20:00,770
Don't be mad.

378
00:20:00,970 --> 00:20:02,050
Stay calm.

379
00:20:05,770 --> 00:20:06,410
He,

380
00:20:06,810 --> 00:20:07,730
I'm afraid I won't

381
00:20:07,770 --> 00:20:08,970
keep up with the training.

382
00:20:09,210 --> 00:20:09,720
Don't worry.

383
00:20:10,050 --> 00:20:10,730
Recruit training

384
00:20:10,810 --> 00:20:11,730
is always gradual.

385
00:20:11,850 --> 00:20:12,890
Day One will be simple.

386
00:20:18,370 --> 00:20:19,130
I can't go on.

387
00:20:19,450 --> 00:20:21,010
I can't go on. I really can't.

388
00:20:26,210 --> 00:20:26,810
On your feet!

389
00:20:27,890 --> 00:20:28,930
Five more laps!

390
00:20:34,170 --> 00:20:35,130
Come on, He.

391
00:20:35,650 --> 00:20:36,450
I'll count to three.

392
00:20:36,570 --> 00:20:37,690
Two, three!

393
00:20:38,610 --> 00:20:39,410
Watch it.

394
00:20:39,810 --> 00:20:40,450
One, two, three.

395
00:20:40,930 --> 00:20:41,490
Let's go.

396
00:20:47,050 --> 00:20:47,730
(I didn't know)

397
00:20:47,810 --> 00:20:49,210
(how Xiao Jue trained his men.)

398
00:20:50,090 --> 00:20:51,650
(I have finally seen it now.)

399
00:20:52,970 --> 00:20:54,730
(It starts so intense right away.)

400
00:20:58,010 --> 00:20:58,610
(Xiao Jue)

401
00:20:59,130 --> 00:21:00,450
(has such a pretty face,)

402
00:21:01,050 --> 00:21:02,130
(but he's truly vicious,)

403
00:21:02,610 --> 00:21:03,490
(just like before.)

404
00:21:05,090 --> 00:21:06,410
(I thought I could earn merits)

405
00:21:06,770 --> 00:21:07,610
(and rise quickly.)

406
00:21:08,410 --> 00:21:09,090
(But Xiao Jue)

407
00:21:09,170 --> 00:21:10,050
(is hard on others)

408
00:21:10,450 --> 00:21:11,450
(and harder on himself.)

409
00:21:15,010 --> 00:21:16,890
(It seems serving under him won't)

410
00:21:17,490 --> 00:21:18,170
(let me rise)

411
00:21:18,770 --> 00:21:19,730
(as easily as I hoped.)

412
00:21:23,450 --> 00:21:25,170
(Severely injured and then poisoned,)

413
00:21:25,770 --> 00:21:26,770
(in bed for a month.)

414
00:21:27,050 --> 00:21:28,650
(It nearly drained all my strength.)

415
00:21:29,410 --> 00:21:30,610
(I can't go on like this.)

416
00:21:35,890 --> 00:21:37,610
Commander, it's only the first day.

417
00:21:38,410 --> 00:21:39,930
Aren't you pushing them too hard?

418
00:21:40,570 --> 00:21:41,250
Mr. Shen,

419
00:21:41,850 --> 00:21:42,770
these recruits

420
00:21:42,970 --> 00:21:44,170
are either country folk

421
00:21:44,330 --> 00:21:45,410
or bandits and thugs.

422
00:21:45,770 --> 00:21:47,130
Like with that horse,

423
00:21:47,690 --> 00:21:49,370
the Commander's harsh methods

424
00:21:49,650 --> 00:21:50,290
aren't about

425
00:21:50,290 --> 00:21:51,290
breaking their spirit.

426
00:21:51,810 --> 00:21:53,490
He's testing their potential.

427
00:21:54,490 --> 00:21:55,330
Mr. Cheng, you know

428
00:21:55,330 --> 00:21:56,090
our Commander well.

429
00:21:59,010 --> 00:22:00,370
Isn't he the horse-taming prodigy

430
00:22:00,370 --> 00:22:01,290
from yesterday?

431
00:22:01,850 --> 00:22:02,650
Why is everyone else

432
00:22:02,650 --> 00:22:03,770
on their seventh lap

433
00:22:04,130 --> 00:22:05,370
while he started his fourth?

434
00:22:05,970 --> 00:22:07,010
In my opinion,

435
00:22:07,330 --> 00:22:08,490
he's lacking in potential.

436
00:22:08,530 --> 00:22:09,050
Don't speak

437
00:22:09,050 --> 00:22:09,930
of my savior that way.

438
00:22:10,170 --> 00:22:10,890
So what if he is?

439
00:22:11,410 --> 00:22:12,210
He could still

440
00:22:12,530 --> 00:22:13,730
make a good army cook.

441
00:22:14,890 --> 00:22:15,690
Army cook?

442
00:22:16,850 --> 00:22:17,770
You underestimate him.

443
00:22:19,890 --> 00:22:20,610
I actually think

444
00:22:21,610 --> 00:22:22,290
he's perfect

445
00:22:22,290 --> 00:22:23,610
scout material.

446
00:22:33,930 --> 00:22:36,610
Now we'll learn to use various weapons.

447
00:22:43,010 --> 00:22:43,770
I can barely stand.

448
00:22:56,210 --> 00:22:56,850
He,

449
00:22:57,370 --> 00:22:58,770
why is your sword so short?

450
00:22:59,290 --> 00:23:00,530
It's not even arm's length.

451
00:23:01,450 --> 00:23:02,370
It's twin blades.

452
00:23:02,850 --> 00:23:03,490
Not a sword,

453
00:23:03,970 --> 00:23:04,730
but a pair.

454
00:23:05,050 --> 00:23:06,930
W-What twin blades?

455
00:23:07,170 --> 00:23:09,050
Real men use this.

456
00:23:10,330 --> 00:23:11,170
So flashy.

457
00:23:11,210 --> 00:23:11,770
Exactly.

458
00:23:12,090 --> 00:23:13,450
Sounds like useless decoration.

459
00:23:42,090 --> 00:23:43,530
- Good.
- Not bad.

460
00:23:43,610 --> 00:23:44,410
He's got skills.

461
00:23:50,290 --> 00:23:51,530
That should be one technique.

462
00:23:52,370 --> 00:23:53,050
That's sad.

463
00:23:53,650 --> 00:23:54,610
He can't fight properly.

464
00:23:59,330 --> 00:24:00,690
I'm exhausted. Need a break.

465
00:24:14,370 --> 00:24:15,050
He's decent.

466
00:24:17,050 --> 00:24:18,130
- Good!
- Good!

467
00:24:18,690 --> 00:24:19,330
(Lei Hou, Yezhou Garrison recruit)
Impressive!

468
00:24:25,050 --> 00:24:26,210
- Good!
- Good!

469
00:24:29,130 --> 00:24:29,970
That's real skill.

470
00:24:36,170 --> 00:24:37,890
A-Are you staring or fighting?

471
00:24:38,770 --> 00:24:39,930
Move back. My turn first.

472
00:24:58,410 --> 00:24:59,050
Impressive!

473
00:24:59,130 --> 00:25:00,170
- Amazing!
- Amazing!

474
00:25:03,610 --> 00:25:04,130
Your turn.

475
00:25:05,450 --> 00:25:06,250
Hurry up.

476
00:25:12,690 --> 00:25:14,370
We're on the clock here.

477
00:25:24,930 --> 00:25:25,730
Draw it back.

478
00:25:25,930 --> 00:25:26,730
Come on.

479
00:25:29,650 --> 00:25:30,170
No need.

480
00:25:30,730 --> 00:25:31,250
I can't pull

481
00:25:31,730 --> 00:25:32,330
this bow.

482
00:25:36,650 --> 00:25:38,170
His stance looked decent.

483
00:25:41,370 --> 00:25:43,010
This bow requires real strength.

484
00:25:44,410 --> 00:25:45,410
We can't blame He Yan.

485
00:25:51,130 --> 00:25:51,690
He,

486
00:25:52,290 --> 00:25:53,290
he excels at everything.

487
00:25:53,650 --> 00:25:54,690
We need to work harder.

488
00:26:06,330 --> 00:26:06,900
Block!

489
00:26:11,810 --> 00:26:12,340
Retract!

490
00:26:15,290 --> 00:26:15,810
Again.

491
00:26:16,370 --> 00:26:16,950
Strike!

492
00:26:19,210 --> 00:26:19,740
Thrust!

493
00:26:23,010 --> 00:26:23,580
Block!

494
00:26:26,450 --> 00:26:27,100
Retract!

495
00:26:28,530 --> 00:26:29,170
Again.

496
00:26:30,010 --> 00:26:30,650
Strike!

497
00:26:32,330 --> 00:26:32,950
Thrust!

498
00:26:34,330 --> 00:26:35,060
Block!

499
00:26:59,170 --> 00:26:59,890
What's funny?

500
00:27:01,330 --> 00:27:02,770
Pick it up. Keep going.

501
00:27:07,290 --> 00:27:08,490
A pretty face with nothing.

502
00:27:08,810 --> 00:27:09,690
All show, no skill.

503
00:27:10,330 --> 00:27:10,970
Retract!

504
00:27:15,130 --> 00:27:15,970
Regardless,

505
00:27:16,210 --> 00:27:17,330
he picked up the spear.

506
00:27:17,610 --> 00:27:18,730
That's commendable.

507
00:27:22,210 --> 00:27:23,650
What did you find about He Yan?

508
00:27:24,130 --> 00:27:25,410
He's from a gatekeeper's family

509
00:27:25,450 --> 00:27:26,010
in Jiazhou.

510
00:27:26,610 --> 00:27:27,730
No prior military history.

511
00:27:28,530 --> 00:27:30,090
No suspicious family connections.

512
00:27:30,810 --> 00:27:31,410
Currently,

513
00:27:31,930 --> 00:27:32,970
his background checks out.

514
00:27:35,690 --> 00:27:37,130
Yet he's skilled in horsemanship

515
00:27:37,730 --> 00:27:39,610
and knows military routines well.

516
00:27:40,570 --> 00:27:41,610
He's clearly a seasoned

517
00:27:41,610 --> 00:27:42,290
soldier.

518
00:27:42,970 --> 00:27:43,730
But during drills,

519
00:27:44,530 --> 00:27:45,690
he performs pathetically.

520
00:27:46,770 --> 00:27:48,170
I'm quite curious.

521
00:27:49,530 --> 00:27:50,450
Is he faking it

522
00:27:51,330 --> 00:27:52,650
or truly useless?

523
00:27:56,650 --> 00:27:57,330
The others?

524
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:58,520
Commander,

525
00:27:59,130 --> 00:28:00,530
recruits have diverse backgrounds.

526
00:28:00,970 --> 00:28:01,690
Some have

527
00:28:01,690 --> 00:28:02,250
dubious pasts.

528
00:28:02,730 --> 00:28:03,900
But the only one who faked it

529
00:28:04,650 --> 00:28:05,290
is this person.

530
00:28:15,410 --> 00:28:16,730
Send two teams from Mingshui.

531
00:28:17,290 --> 00:28:18,170
One to Jiazhou

532
00:28:18,690 --> 00:28:20,090
and one to Que City.

533
00:28:21,370 --> 00:28:22,970
Investigate this impostor thoroughly.

534
00:28:24,090 --> 00:28:24,650
The rest

535
00:28:26,050 --> 00:28:27,490
continue investigating in Mingshui.

536
00:28:28,450 --> 00:28:29,210
As you command.

537
00:28:34,190 --> 00:28:37,560
(Longevity of Cranes and Pines)

538
00:28:44,490 --> 00:28:47,130
(Song Wan, Xiao Jue's Mother)

539
00:29:51,090 --> 00:29:51,890
What's that smell?

540
00:29:54,970 --> 00:29:55,810
It seems to be

541
00:29:55,970 --> 00:29:57,050
from the mountain pass.

542
00:30:00,610 --> 00:30:01,730
The smell of sulfur?

543
00:30:03,770 --> 00:30:04,610
A hot spring?

544
00:30:35,410 --> 00:30:36,210
(But, Sister,)

545
00:30:36,610 --> 00:30:37,970
(the achievements you have today)

546
00:30:38,650 --> 00:30:39,450
are entirely due to

547
00:30:39,730 --> 00:30:42,210
your identity
as the He family's legitimate heir.

548
00:30:42,770 --> 00:30:44,250
(Even with the name He Rufei,)

549
00:30:44,450 --> 00:30:46,250
as a woman,

550
00:30:47,090 --> 00:30:47,850
how could you

551
00:30:48,290 --> 00:30:50,210
(achieve such accomplishments
and reputation?)

552
00:30:53,090 --> 00:30:54,090
(Those were all earned)

553
00:30:54,090 --> 00:30:55,770
(through my pain, blood, and tears.)

554
00:30:57,650 --> 00:30:59,010
(The He family's heir)

555
00:31:00,330 --> 00:31:02,290
(are just empty words.)

556
00:31:04,210 --> 00:31:04,850
(What's mine)

557
00:31:06,090 --> 00:31:07,090
(can't be taken away.)

558
00:31:22,650 --> 00:31:23,730
Only months have passed.

559
00:31:24,810 --> 00:31:26,330
But it feels like a lifetime ago.

560
00:31:28,610 --> 00:31:30,370
In my past life, I hid in shadows.

561
00:31:31,610 --> 00:31:33,570
Only the moon saw my true face.

562
00:31:36,010 --> 00:31:36,930
In this life,

563
00:31:38,570 --> 00:31:39,810
I can finally

564
00:31:40,890 --> 00:31:42,970
fight with honor.

565
00:31:49,130 --> 00:31:50,210
(With this hot spring)

566
00:31:50,890 --> 00:31:51,890
(and proper training,)

567
00:31:52,890 --> 00:31:54,090
(I should recover completely)

568
00:31:54,290 --> 00:31:55,090
(in a few days.)

569
00:33:06,060 --> 00:33:08,220
♪Light shines upon my heart♪

570
00:33:08,320 --> 00:33:12,240
♪Unveiling scars,
I choose to swim upstream♪

571
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:14,360
♪The resonance of courage
rings loud and clear♪

572
00:33:14,450 --> 00:33:19,380
♪It's the boldness
that defines existence♪

573
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:32,890
♪I've seen the mountains♪

574
00:33:33,090 --> 00:33:34,500
♪And trodden through ice♪

575
00:33:34,770 --> 00:33:37,580
♪Day after day, I venture alone♪

576
00:33:37,890 --> 00:33:39,280
♪Destiny is my creed♪

577
00:33:39,340 --> 00:33:40,740
♪Ideals surge beneath the surface♪

578
00:33:40,890 --> 00:33:42,680
♪Igniting the flame against the winds♪

579
00:33:43,880 --> 00:33:45,350
♪A restless yearning in my soul♪

580
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:46,810
♪Gazing through the mire♪

581
00:33:46,990 --> 00:33:49,380
♪Who cares about this boundless void♪

582
00:33:49,580 --> 00:33:51,630
♪Charge ahead with blazing fervor♪

583
00:33:52,760 --> 00:33:54,590
♪Stubbornly fighting with my life♪

584
